SourceEntity.a:_sQL: ALTER function dbo.UnpivotTIndex( @accountID bigint, @canvasID uniqueidentifier = null, @teamID uniqueidentifier, @lastUpdated datetimeoffset = null, @InstrumentID as UniqueIdentifier, @TransactionDate Date, @TransactionID UniqueIdentifier) RETURNS TABLE as RETURN ( select ID,ValueIndex,IndexRef,replace(replace(ValueIndex,'Value',''),'IndexID','') as LineID from ( SELECT ID,ValueIndex,IndexRef FROM (select ID,Value1IndexID, Value2IndexID, Value3IndexID, Value4IndexID, Value5IndexID, Value6IndexID, Value7IndexID, Value8IndexID, Value9IndexID, Value10IndexID, Value11IndexID, Value12IndexID, Value13IndexID, Value14IndexID, Value15IndexID, Value16IndexID, Value17IndexID, Value18IndexID, Value19IndexID, Value20IndexID -- Test to filter the transactions from fn_Transactions(@accountID, @canvasID, @teamID, @lastUpdated) where InstrumentID = @InstrumentID and Status <> 3 and TransactionDate <= @TransactionDate -- This is a non used GUID and ID <> coalesce(@TransactionID,'7A0A69B0-C3A4-454C-A1F2-057B7320DECD') ) p UNPIVOT ( IndexRef for ValueIndex in (Value1IndexID, Value2IndexID, Value3IndexID, Value4IndexID, Value5IndexID, Value6IndexID, Value7IndexID, Value8IndexID, Value9IndexID, Value10IndexID, Value11IndexID, Value12IndexID, Value13IndexID, Value14IndexID, Value15IndexID, Value16IndexID, Value17IndexID, Value18IndexID, Value19IndexID, Value20IndexID) ) as unpvt ) as unpivoted )

ALTER function dbo.UnpivotTLocal( @accountID bigint, @canvasID uniqueidentifier = null, @teamID uniqueidentifier, @lastUpdated datetimeoffset = null, @InstrumentID as UniqueIdentifier, @TransactionDate Date, @TransactionID UniqueIdentifier) RETURNS TABLE as RETURN ( select ID,LocalValue,Amount as LocalAmount,replace(LocalValue,'LocalValue','') as LineID from ( -- Unpivot Local Values SELECT ID, LocalValue,Amount FROM (select ID, LocalValue1, LocalValue2, LocalValue3, LocalValue4, LocalValue5, LocalValue6, LocalValue7, LocalValue8, LocalValue9, LocalValue10, LocalValue11, LocalValue12, LocalValue13, LocalValue14, LocalValue15, LocalValue16, LocalValue17, LocalValue18, LocalValue19, LocalValue20 -- Test to filter the transactions from fn_Transactions(@accountID, @canvasID, @teamID, @lastUpdated) where InstrumentID = @InstrumentID and Status <> 3 and TransactionDate <= @TransactionDate -- This is a non used GUID and ID <> coalesce(@TransactionID,'7A0A69B0-C3A4-454C-A1F2-057B7320DECD') ) p UNPIVOT ( Amount for LocalValue in (LocalValue1, LocalValue2, LocalValue3, LocalValue4, LocalValue5, LocalValue6, LocalValue7, LocalValue8, LocalValue9, LocalValue10, LocalValue11, LocalValue12, LocalValue13, LocalValue14, LocalValue15, LocalValue16, LocalValue17, LocalValue18, LocalValue19, LocalValue20) ) as unpvt ) unpivoted )
